      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "optimalisation suggestion: precompile the pattern once : private static final Pattern EOL_PATTERN=Pattern.compile(&quot;...&quot;); outside the method. And use it in the method: Matcher m =EOL_PATTERN.matcher(yourinput);"
