    "question_id" : 2850203,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you use Java 8 then:</p>\n\n<pre><code>long lines = stringWithNewlines.chars().filter(x -&gt; x == '\\n').count() + 1;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>(+1 in the end is to count last line if string is trimmed)</p>\n\n<p>One line solution</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 1939636,
      "reputation" : 32733,
      "user_id" : 1746118,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 95,
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/dea2252138dd9905af87cd6803fb5665?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
